  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this trial is to investigate whether thermal ablation EMR with soft&#xD;
      tip snare coagulation (STSC) reduces the recurrence rate of lateral spreading or sessile&#xD;
      polyps ≥20mm compared to standard EMR.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
