  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Proven colorectal sessile or lateral spreading polyps with a diameter of ≥ 20mm&#xD;
             requiring piecemeal resection with EMR.&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Previously attempted intervention&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Polyps with any signs of invasive malignancy&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Presence or suspicion of inflammatory bowel disease&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  En bloc resection&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Incomplete resection&#xD;
      </textblock>
